ow. If you have a lot of logs, place make a paste bin with your logs and share the link with us here: -->\r\n<!-- ‚úçÔ∏è-->\r\n\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n\r\n## üåç  Your Environment\r\n\r\n**Operating System:**\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n  <code>\r\nUbuntu 20.04\r\n  </code>\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n**What version of Prysm are you running? (Which release)**\r\n\r\ncompiled from master with `bazel build //beacon-chain:beacon-chain --config=release`\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n  <code>\r\nPrysm/v1.0.0-beta.0.rc/544dac298aa5bca9ead72559737c77c45ab1a79a\r\n  </code>\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n**Anything else relevant (validator index / public key)?**\r\n\r\n",
